name: Elysian fields
description:
(Post Mortem-2021)
What awaits us at the end of the long pilgrimage that is life? perhaps a promised land like the one described in the champs elysées, made of lush grass, poppies and prosperity or perhaps a land of pain, suffering and blood? or maybe both things await us one after the other, in the form of a land that first gives you hope and then destroys it and then starts again day after day, maybe it would be the right punishment for a life like ours
